<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/110/314/s204/b/4/E">Pub. L. 110–314, § 204(b)(4)(E)</ref>, substituted “Commission” for “Secretary of Health, Education, and Welfare” in two places.</p>
